    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Photos of preserved specimens of species in the family Caudinidae Heding, 1931: a, Hedingia glabra (Théel, 1886) (NIWA 64078); b, Paracaudina alta sp. nov. (NIWA 68129); c, Paracaudina chilensis (Müller, 1850) (NIWA 77411); d, Paracaudina coriacea (Hutton, 1872) (NIWA 70954); e, Paracaudina coriacea (Hutton, 1872) lectotype (NHMUK 98.10.8.1.2); f, Paracaudina reductia sp. nov. (NIWA 70957)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/223159/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

